Maria Kukucova was arrested in April last year after former partner Andy Bush was found shot to death in his rented holiday villa on the Costa del Sol in southern Spain . 
  The Slovakian model had gone on the run but was tracked down in her home town of Nova Basoca . 
  Her parents Lubomir Kukuca and Danka are being forced to sell their home to pay thousands for her lawyers' fees . 
  Mr Bush, 48 , was found dead in his villa after being shot in the back of the head . 
  Now her parents say they feel hated in their own village . 
 